Class FlipFitCustomer

java.lang.Object
com.flipkart.bean.FlipFitUser
com.flipkart.bean.FlipFitCustomer
public class FlipFitCustomer extends FlipFitUser
Represents a customer in the FlipFit system, extending FlipFitUser. Contains customer-specific details such as phone number and card details.
Author:
gamma-group
